                     <interp inst="t17830430-57-off315" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830430-57-off315" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously and feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17830430-57-victim724" type="victimName">
                           Robert 
