                  , about the hour of eight in the night, on the <rs id="t17830430-57-cd316" type="crimeDate">22d day of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830430-57-off315 t17830430-57-cd316"></join> last, and burglariously stealing therein, one wooden box, value 6 d. one white muslin jacket, value 2 s. one white muslin petticoat, value 2 s. one cotton gown, value 1 s. one dimity petticoat, value 1 s. one stuff petticoat, value 1 s. and two linen aprons, value 2 s.
